official_title: To repeal the provisions of the Patient Protection and Affordable Care Act providing for the Independent Payment Advisory Board.
short_title: Protecting Seniors' Access to Medicare Act of 2017

summary.text:
Protecting Seniors' Access to Medicare Act of 2017

This bill amends the Patient Protection and Affordable Care Act (PPACA) to terminate the Independent Payment Advisory Board (IPAB). Under the PPACA, the IPAB is tasked with developing proposals to reduce the per capital rate of growth in Medicare spending.
